      "features": [
        {
          "type": "FeatureText",
          "properties": {
            "text": "Baby\u0027s First Base!\n\nWhen you start the game, you are thrown into a world with pretty much nothing, and no clue where to go. The quest book will give you guidance on the first things to do, but there is a nagging problem overhead: the sun. It will set, darkness will fall, and all the riff-raff will come out and turn you into paste.\n\nLet\u0027s find some shelter . . . fast!",
            "wrap": 0,
            "size": 1.0,
            "color": "FF555555",
            "xPos": 31,
            "yPos": 23,
            "width": 163.0,
            "height": 177.0
          }
        },
        {
          "type": "FeatureText",
          "properties": {
            "text": "You would first think to build a base: a house, a castle, a whatever. However, the easiest thing to do for the first nights is to dig in somewhere. If all else fails, you can probably just dig straight down and weather out the first night. Just start making torches and work on getting the starters tools. On sunrise, you can crawl out with your stuff and renew your search.\n\nHere are some examples of places you might want to consider staging yourself for most of the game.",
            "wrap": 0,
            "size": 1.0,
            "color": "FF555555",
            "xPos": 229,
            "yPos": 21,
            "width": 167.0,
            "height": 174.0
          }
        }
      ],
      "pageName": ""
    },
    {
      "features": [
        {
          "type": "FeatureImage",
          "properties": {
