            "height": 111.0
          }
        },
        {
          "type": "FeatureText",
          "properties": {
            "text": "Islands\n\nGetting away might mean finding your own little island. Build a boat, find the ocean, and just bumble around. You can do this even when the sun sets, as monsters can\u0027t hit you in the sea!",
            "wrap": 0,
            "size": 1.0,
            "color": "FF555555",
            "xPos": 27,
            "yPos": 131,
            "width": 173.0,
            "height": 69.0
          }
        },
        {
          "type": "FeatureText",
          "properties": {
            "text": "+ Usually Islands are flat\n+ It\u0027s easy to secure the island  with torches\n+ You can boat out to other interesting areas",
            "wrap": 0,
            "size": 1.0,
            "color": "FF555555",
            "xPos": 224,
            "yPos": 131,
            "width": 102.0,
            "height": 52.0
