        {
          "type": "FeatureText",
          "properties": {
            "text": "Cliff Face\n\nLook at the map for sharp gradients, and you may find a usable cliff. Bonus points if it has caves. In this case, you don\u0027t have to dig down, you can just dig in.",
            "wrap": 0,
            "size": 1.0,
            "color": "FF555555",
            "xPos": 26,
            "yPos": 128,
            "width": 176.0,
            "height": 68.0
          }
        },
        {
          "type": "FeatureText",
          "properties": {
            "text": "+ Really easy to spot\n+ Simple to get started",
            "wrap": 0,
            "size": 1.0,
            "color": "FF555555",
            "xPos": 222,
            "yPos": 127,
            "width": 83.0,
            "height": 80.0
          }
        },
        {
          "type": "FeatureText",
          "properties": {
            "text": "- Implies higher elevations that might be missing stuff you need\n- Usually you have to do all the hard work manually",
            "wrap": 0,
