          "type": "FeatureText",
          "properties": {
            "text": "Jumbo Redwood\n\nClimb up a redwood and beat up leaves until you get 4 saplings. Then get bone meal. Lay out the saplings ~6 blocks apart in a + sign, and spray with bone meal. Have a hatchet ready in case you get trapped!",
            "wrap": 0,
            "size": 1.0,
            "color": "FF555555",
            "xPos": 34,
            "yPos": 125,
            "width": 175.0,
            "height": 67.0
          }
        },
        {
          "type": "FeatureText",
          "properties": {
            "text": "+ More Spacious\n+ Even more wood\n+ If done well, you can make an inner chamber automatically",
            "wrap": 0,
            "size": 1.0,
            "color": "FF555555",
