        {
          "type": "FeatureText",
          "properties": {
            "text": "Villages\n\nDON\u0027T DO IT! You don\u0027t have the materials to secure the village and you will just invite the zombie apocalypse as the villagers get taken.",
            "wrap": 0,
            "size": 1.0,
            "color": "FF555555",
            "xPos": 26,
            "yPos": 136,
            "width": 174.0,
            "height": 59.0
          }
        },
        {
          "type": "FeatureText",
          "properties": {
            "text": "If you must, then set up a quarry out of site of the village, and acquire enough torches and walls that you can pen the entire plance in.\n\nHowever, what you really should do is steal their smeltery, if they have one. Look at this poor smeltery! It is overgrown with trees and sheep! It just needs a controller and a tank to be fully-functional. Also, steal all the stuff in their chests. Muahahaha!",
            "wrap": 0,
